[30;1m148 | [0m[35m        least one chunk is in use. If one chunk is in use, those bytes are[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m3166[0m[34m of [0m[33m3283[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000704[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.DataExfiltration.Hostname[0m
  Severity: [36mImportant[0m, Confidence: [36mLow[0m
  Filename: [33m/oracledb-3.1.0/src/oracledb/connect_params.py[0m
   Pattern: [32m.hostname[0m
[30;1m998 | [0m[35m          matched with the server. This value is ignored if the[0m
[30;1m999 | [0m[35m          ssl_server_dn_match parameter is not set to the value True. If[0m
[30;1m1000 | [0m[35m          specified this value is used for any verfication. Otherwise the[0m
[30;1m1001 | [0m[35m          hostname will be used[0m
[30;1m1002 | [0m[35m[0m
